steps.html_instructions:
Turn left onto Şair Eşref Cd./D950
Continue to follow D950

Turn left onto Bingöl - Elazığ Yolu/D300
Continue to follow D300
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Karakoçan Yolu
At the roundabout, continue straight onto Kığı Cd.
Aşağıdoluca Köyü Yolu turns slightly left and becomes Yukarıdoluca Köyü Yolu

Turn right onto Erzincan Tunceli Yolu/D885
Continue to follow D885

Make a U-turn
Continue to follow D100/E80
Take the exit on the left toward Sivas Erzincan Yolu
Keep right at the fork to continue toward Sivas Erzincan Yolu

Continue onto Amasya Erzincan Yolu/D100/E80
Continue to follow D100/E80

Keep left to continue on Samsun Amasya Yolu/İstiklal Cd./D100/E80
Continue to follow Samsun Amasya Yolu/D100/E80

Keep left at the fork and merge onto Samsun Çorum Yolu/D100/E80
Continue to follow D100/E80

Turn right onto Çorum Kastamonu Yolu/D775
Continue to follow D775

Make a U-turn
Continue to follow Cumhuriyet Cd.
Destination will be on the left
